description: Energy Today Inc., an independent energy company, focuses on the acquisition, exploration, exploitation, and production of natural gas and crude oil worldwide. It has interests in the oil and gas leases in western Ukraine. The company was formerly known as Yellow7, Inc. and changed its name to Energy Today, Inc. in April 2013. Energy Today, Inc. is based in Manchester, New Hampshire. Energy Today Inc. is a subsidiary of QED Connect, Inc.
